---
title: Saucy Spanish-Style Beef Meatballs with Garlic Veggie Couscous & Parsley
description: These beef meatballs are bursting with bright flavours, coated in a tomato-based and veggie-filled sauce. Sitting atop a bed of fluffy garlic couscous to soak up all of that goodness, what more could you possibly want?

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
